French fisherman survives after crocodile bites down on his head , tries ‘ death roll ’ Associated Press | 13 / 04 / 22 | Last Updated : 13 / 04 / 22 10 : 47 AM ETMore from Associated Press Twitter Google + LinkedIn Email Comments More Tumblr Pinterest Reddit Digg FarkIt StumbleUpon DARWIN , Australia — A French fisherman was bloodied but back on his fishing boat Monday , just hours after he escaped from the jaws of a young saltwater crocodile who attacked him while swimming along a remote stretch of Australia ’ s northern coast .